  "doc_id": "47036",
  "text": "Human neuroblastoma cell line SH-SY5Y that stably expressed wild type Tau (2N4R, 1-411; kindly provided by Roger M. Nitsch) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] or human embryonic kidney 293 cell line (HEK293) cells were maintained in a 5% CO2 humid atmosphere at 37°C in Dulbecco's modified eagle medium/Ham's F12 nutrient mixture (DMEM/F12) with 10% fetal bovine serum, 10 U/ml penicillin, and 10 µg/ml streptomycin (all from Life technologies) as described [CITATION_3] .",
